NK013(pa)003:0: dpal gsang ba snying po sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rtsa
NK013(pa)003:1: ba'i rgyud 'chad thabs kyi cho ga'i rim pa o
NK013(pa)003:2: rgyan smin grol gling gi khri chen pad+ma dbang rgyal
NK013(pa)003:4: na mo gu ru b+h+yah rgyud kyi 'chad nyan tshugs
NK013(pa)003:5: pa'i nyin thog mar slob dpon gyis tshig bdun gsol
NK013(pa)003:6: 'debs dang / rnam thar gsol 'debs sngon du 'gro
NK013(pa)003:7: bas tshogs zhing badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs spyan drangs nas
NK013(pa)003:8: rgyun bshags bya ba nas bzung 'das gtor bsngo ba'i
NK013(pa)003:9: bar zab don snang ba bzhin btang /
NK013(pa)003:10: gtor bsngosa legs ldan gter gzhi bshags phrin rjes grol /
NK013(pa)003:11: slob ma rnams 'dus pa dang thams cad sdeb 'don gyis tshig bdun gsol 'debs dang /
NK013(pa)003:12: spros bral chos dbyings lhu gsum gyi rjes /
NK013(pa)003:13: mtsho skyes sprul skus lung bstan rjes bzung zhing //
NK013(pa)003:20: rdo rje slob dpon sogs rgyun bshags lan gcig gi rjes su slob dpon gyis /
NK013(pa)003:21: so so rang rang gi dbu gtsug tu pam las
NK013(pa)003:22: pad+ma dang a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng
NK013(pa)003:23: du h+aum yig re re 'od du zhu ba las
NK013(pa)003:24: bla ma rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog dkar po
NK013(pa)003:26: phyag g.yas gser gyi rdo rje rtse lnga pa thugs kar gtod cing 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)003:27: g.yon dngul dkar gyi dril bu dku la brten pa /
NK013(pa)003:28: zhabs sems dpa'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa dar dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK013(pa)003:29: yum snyems ma dkar mo dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i
NK013(pa)003:30: skur gyur pa'i yab kyi thugs kar zla ba'i dkyil
NK013(pa)003:31: 'khor gyi steng du h+aum yig dkar po gsal zhing
NK013(pa)003:32: 'tsher ba / de'i mtha' bskor du yi ge brgya
NK013(pa)003:33: pa'i sngags phreng dri ma med pas g.yas su bskor
NK013(pa)003:34: 'tsher ba / bar bsam la / spyi bo'i bla
NK013(pa)003:35: ma rdo rje sems dpa' la mos gus gdung shugs
NK013(pa)003:36: drag pos yi ge brgya pa gsol 'debs kyi tshul
NK013(pa)003:37: du bzlas pas thugs ka'i sngags phreng dang sku'i cha
NK013(pa)003:38: thams cad las bdud rtsi dkar po'i chu rgyun skya
NK013(pa)003:39: chil chil babs pa rang gi spyi bo nas zhugs
NK013(pa)003:40: 'tsher ba / bar bsam la / / lus nang
NK013(pa)003:41: gi nad gdon sdig sgrib thams cad sangs kyis dag
NK013(pa)003:43: gsung thugs ye shes rdo rje'i dbang bzhi rdzogs su
NK013(pa)003:44: thob ste thugs rgyud byin gyis brlabs par gyur snyam
NK013(pa)003:45: pas yi ge brgya pa gsol 'debs kyi tshul du
NK013(pa)003:47: zhes yig brgya mang zhig bzla /
NK013(pa)003:48: mgon po bdag ni sogs nas mdzad du gsol //
NK013(pa)003:50: de ltar gsol ba btab pas spyi bo'i bla ma
NK013(pa)003:51: rdo rje sems dpa' 'od du zhu nas so so
NK013(pa)003:52: rang rang la thim par gyur /
NK013(pa)003:53: de nas slob dpon gyi lce'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus dang /
NK013(pa)003:54: so so rang rang gi snyan gyi 'doms rtsa gnyis
NK013(pa)003:55: su b+h+r+aum yig dmar ser re re 'od du zhu
NK013(pa)003:56: ba las / 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i gzhal yas
NK013(pa)003:57: khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa gdan dang bcas pa
NK013(pa)003:59: de nas slob dpon gyi lce'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus
NK013(pa)003:60: su h+r+aihzunga zhu bar gyur pa las snang ba mtha'
NK013(pa)003:61: yas dmar po g.yas pad+ma dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin
NK013(pa)003:62: pa yum gos dkar mo dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i
NK013(pa)003:63: skur gyur / rtsibs bzhi'i shar nas rim pa bzhin
NK013(pa)003:64: h+r+aihyiga zung re zhu ba yongs su gyur pa las
NK013(pa)003:65: skur gyur / / rdo rje chos dang rdo rje pi wang ma /
NK013(pa)003:66: rdo rje rnon po dang rdo rje me sgron ma /
NK013(pa)003:67: rdo rje 'khor lo dang rdo rje lcags sgrog ma /
NK013(pa)003:68: rdo rje smra ba dang rdo rje gsal bkra ma ste /
NK013(pa)003:69: thams cad kyang sku mdog dmar gsal zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'i rnam pa can du gyur /
NK013(pa)003:70: so so'i snyan gyi dkyil 'khor cha gnyis kyi dbus
NK013(pa)003:71: su t+r+aam yig zung re zhu ba yongs su gyur
NK013(pa)003:72: pa las / rin chen 'byung gnas ser po g.yas
NK013(pa)003:73: rin po che dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa yum
NK013(pa)003:74: m+aa ma k+ai dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i skur gyur
NK013(pa)003:75: pa las / / rtsibs bzhi'i shar nas rim pa
NK013(pa)003:76: bzhin t+r+aam zung re zhu ba yongs su gyur pa
NK013(pa)003:77: pa las / / las / rdo rje rin po che dang rdo rje m+aa l+ye ma /
NK013(pa)003:78: rdo rje nyi ma dang rdo rje me tog ma /
NK013(pa)003:79: rdo rje rgyal mtshan dang rdo rje zhags pa ma /
NK013(pa)003:80: rdo rje bzhad pa dang rdo rje bde ba ma ste /
NK013(pa)003:81: thams cad kyang sku mdog gser btso ma lta bu zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'i skur gyur /
NK013(pa)003:82: de ltar dkyil 'khor cha gsum ka'i sgo bzhir h+aum dzah h+aum h+aum /
NK013(pa)003:84: h+aum hoh zhes pas shar sgor gshin rje gshed /
NK013(pa)003:87: byang sgor bdud rtsi 'khyil ba rnams rang rang gi
NK013(pa)003:88: yum lcags kyu ma la sogs pa dang mnyam par
NK013(pa)003:90: de nas slob dpon gyi lce yi dkyil 'khor la dbang bskur bar gyur /
NK013(pa)003:91: ma h+aa pra t+ye bek+sha na sogs sngags tshan lnga /
NK013(pa)003:92: slar yang snyan gyi dkyil 'khor la dbang bskur bar gyur /
NK013(pa)003:93: ma h+aa sa ma t+aa sogs lngas bskur /
NK013(pa)003:94: dkyil 'khor cha gsum ka'i gnas gsum byin gyis brlabs par gyur /
NK013(pa)003:95: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya sogs /
NK013(pa)003:96: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah e h+ye hi dzahh+aum bam hoh
NK013(pa)003:97: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+rasa brtan par byas
NK013(pa)003:98: nas / kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod nas /
NK013(pa)003:99: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK013(pa)003:100: zhes brjod pas lha tshogs thams cad 'od du zhu
NK013(pa)003:101: ba'i rkyen gyis slob bu yang 'od du zhu ba
NK013(pa)003:102: 'od phung ser po las rin chen 'byung gnas dang
NK013(pa)003:103: / slob dpon 'od du zhu ba 'od phung dmar
NK013(pa)003:104: po las de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsung
NK013(pa)003:105: rdo rje'i bdag nyid snang ba mtha' yas kyi skur
NK013(pa)003:107: zhes brjod rjes bdud tshar gcod kyi sngags tshar gcig 'don /
NK013(pa)003:108: de nas rim par lo rgyus nas 'chad par mdzad cing /
NK013(pa)003:111: sha mi sha ma wa ti /
NK013(pa)003:120: bi shud+d+he nirma le s+aa la pa na ye /
NK013(pa)003:131: sarba p+aa ra pra w+aa di na /
NK013(pa)003:132: bi muk+ta m+aa ra p+aa sha /
NK013(pa)003:143: bsod nams 'di yis sogs dge ba bsngo bar mdzad /
NK013(pa)003:145: bla ma yi dam lha tshogs dgongs su gsol //
NK013(pa)003:147: phun tshogs mtha' dag yid bzhin 'byor gyur cig /
NK013(pa)003:149: rgyal ba kun gyi gsang chen sogs /
NK013(pa)003:152: mi 'gyur lhun po sogs kyis shis brjod cing /
NK013(pa)003:153: de ltar 'grub par byed pa yang sogs bya /
NK013(pa)003:154: slob dpon gyis chos skyong gtor 'bul sogs rjes chog mtha' rgyas su mdzad pa yin no //
NK013(pa)003:155: zhes pa 'di smyos rigs dge sbyor kun bzang /
NK013(pa)003:158: chos mdzad kun ldan nas chos 'chad slob dpon dus
NK013(pa)003:159: lha rdzas dang rin gnyis kyi skyes bcas bskul ma
NK013(pa)003:160: gnang ba bzhin / snga dus ji ltar mdzad pa'i
NK013(pa)003:161: chog khrigs khungs ma nyid la brten nas zin bris
